fm: ListNode* addTwoNumbers(ListNode* l1, ListNode* l2) {     ListNode* curr = new ListNode();     ListNode* temp = curr;      int carry = 0;      while (l1 != NULL || l2 != NULL || carry) {       int sum = 0;       if (l1 != NULL) {         sum += l1->val;         l1 = l1->next;       }       if (l2 != NULL) {         sum += l2->val;         l2 = l2->next;       }       sum += carry;       carry = sum / 10;       ListNode* node = new ListNode(sum % 10);       temp->next = node;       temp = temp->next;     }      return curr->next;   }

fm: double findMedianSortedArrays(vector<int>& nums1, vector<int>& nums2) {     int n = nums1.size() + nums2.size();      nums1.insert(nums1.end(), nums2.begin(), nums2.end());      sort(nums1.begin(), nums1.end());      if (n % 2 == 0) {       return (nums1[n / 2 - 1] + nums1[n / 2]) / 2.0;     } else {       return nums1[n / 2];     }   }

fm: int reverse(int x) {     int temp = abs(x);     long long ans = 0;     while (temp > 0) {       ans = ans * 10 + temp % 10;       temp /= 10;     }     if (x > 0)       return ans > INT_MAX || ans < INT_MIN ? 0 : ans;     else       return ans > INT_MAX || ans < INT_MIN ? 0 : -(ans);   }
